  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The continuation of the Find All series in the Find All 6: Netherlands genre. Immerse yourself in another exciting journey and find many different hidden objects while enjoying the views of an ancient village, a colorful waterfront and a hot resort. Finding the necessary items will make the black and white world with its inhabitants come to life. It's up to you to decide which items you want to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 750 search items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Option to choose the desired item to search for</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Increasing level of difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- There is a hint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interactivity. Items can be searched inside buildings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The world is populated with inhabitants, each one has its own story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Coloring levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2.5D effect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Chance to meet Meowogog</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The continuation of the Find All series in the Find All 6: Netherlands genre. Immerse yourself in another exciting journey and find many different hidden objects while enjoying the views of an ancient village, a colorful waterfront and a hot resort. Finding the necessary items will make the black and white world with its inhabitants come to life. It's up to you to decide which items you want to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 750 search items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Option to choose the desired item to search for</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Increasing level of difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- There is a hint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interactivity. Items can be searched inside buildings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The world is populated with inhabitants, each one has its own story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Coloring levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2.5D effect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Chance to meet Meowogog</p>",
